{"type":null,"faqId":33503,"title":"如何利用情景智能设置生日提醒？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.38402778in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">首先需开启情景智能中的生日提醒：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">下拉通知栏，点击时间右侧的情景智能按钮，进入“情景智能”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span class=\"s1\">打开右上角设置按钮，在“事项提醒”中打开“生日”开关。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=106145\" style=\"width:2.3895833in;height:4.25in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=106146\" style=\"width:2.3888888in;height:4.2472224in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=106147\" style=\"width:2.395139in;height:4.258333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=106148\" style=\"width:2.3923612in;height:4.2520833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">然后在联系人界面创建生日记录：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">在“联系人”界面，选择需要创建提醒的联系人，点击“编辑”进入编辑界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击“添加其他项”&gt; “生日”，然后选择年月日信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击“完成”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击屏幕右上方的“√”，完成保存。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">设置成功后，到了联系人生日前一天，会有提示：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=106149\" style=\"width:2.1354167in;height:3.7958333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=106150\" style=\"width:2.1444445in;height:3.8138888in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=106151\" style=\"width:2.1354167in;height:3.7965279in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8223","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748635000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":13,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"情景智能,设置,生日提醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}